---
title: Telegram Bot Overview
---
flowchart TD
    U[Пользователь] --> TG[Telegram]
    TG --> GW[bot-gateway]

    GW --> RL[Redis rate limit]
    GW --> DU[Redis duplicate update check]
    GW --> FSM[Redis user session state]

    GW --> MENU[Главное меню]

    MENU --> B[Создать бронь]
    MENU --> MB[Мои брони]
    MENU --> C[Календарь]
    MENU --> A[Админ действия]
    MENU --> H[Помощь]

    B --> BK[booking-service]
    B --> PAY[payment-service, если нужна оплата]
    MB --> BK
    C --> CAL[calendar-service]
    A --> ADM[admin-service]

    BK --> PG[(PostgreSQL)]
    PAY --> PG
    CAL --> PG
    ADM --> PG

    BK --> RS[(Redis Streams)]
    PAY --> RS
    ADM --> RS

    RS --> NOT[notification-service]
    NOT --> TG

    GW -.-> SEC[Подписывает internal HTTP: HMAC + request id + user signature]
    BK -.-> AUD[audit log]
    PAY -.-> AUD
    ADM -.-> AUD
    AUD --> PG
